      <p class="lead">Discover how video enhances B2B lead generation, with effective strategies and real success stories from Viven's engaging video solutions.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>July 3, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 25, 2025</span></p>
